<p>Go to Sol A and take on the goblins in there.&nbsp;&nbsp;they drop a lot of fine steel weapons, and also the fiery ore.  You can use the FS to make HQ ore, and the fiery can make fire-forged weapons.  just need fiery temper, which is made from drops from lavastorm mobs.  Also, in Sol A you can get unrefined ores, and there is a quest that rewards with plat and faction.  A gnome in the bazaar (no idea where he is now) would reward with 14pp for 4 small bricks and 44pp for 4 large bricks.  The goblins drop these also.</p>
